textfsm_template:
Value ICMP_SEQ (\d+)
Value TTL (\d+)
Value TIME ([-+]?[0-9]*\.?[0-9]+)
Value PACKETS_TRANSMITTED (\d+)
Value PACKETS_RECEIVED (\d+)
Value PACKET_LOSS (\d+%)
Value TIME_MS (\d+)
Value RTT_MIN ([-+]?[0-9]*\.?[0-9]+)
Value RTT_AVG ([-+]?[0-9]*\.?[0-9]+)
Value RTT_MAX ([-+]?[0-9]*\.?[0-9]+)
Value RTT_MDEV ([-+]?[0-9]*\.?[0-9]+)

Start
  ^64 bytes from.*icmp_seq=${ICMP_SEQ}\ ttl=${TTL}\ time=${TIME}\ ms
  ^---.*ping statistics ---
  ^${PACKETS_TRANSMITTED} packets transmitted, ${PACKETS_RECEIVED} received, ${PACKET_LOSS} packet loss, time ${TIME_MS}ms
  ^rtt\ min/avg/max/mdev\ =\ ${RTT_MIN}/${RTT_AVG}/${RTT_MAX}/${RTT_MDEV}\ ms
